---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - TopOnlineForm">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white p-6 md:p-10 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-t-4 border-red-600">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 border-b pb-2">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>TopOnlineForm.com</strong>, India's fastest-growing education and career portal. Our mission is to provide the latest updates on Government Jobs (Sarkari Naukri), Competitive Exams, Admit Cards, Results, and Answer Keys to students across India.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        We understand the struggle of finding accurate job notifications on time. Our dedicated team works 24/7 to track official government websites and deliver simplified, easy-to-understand information directly to you.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-4">What We Provide?</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>Latest Sarkari Result and Job Notifications.</li>
        <li>Instant Admit Card download links.</li>
        <li>Exam Syllabus and Pattern details.</li>
        <li>Admission forms for Universities (B.Ed, PhD, UG/PG).</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="mt-4">
        Thank you for trusting TopOnlineForm.com. If you have any suggestions, feel free to contact us.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
